.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
City: nizza, edinburgh, liverpool, miami
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, horse, hamster
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the person traveling to miami is the owner of the horse##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to edinburgh##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| City   | edinburgh     | liverpool           | nizza | miami  |
| Pet         | chinchilla | hamster | pony   | horse |

