.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, chess, cooking, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, thriller, disaster, musical
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | skydiving   | chess | reading | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre     | disaster | martial-arts    | thriller  | musical |

