2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the chef##1
3. the architect is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the fish is between the doctor and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Job    | manager   | chef      | doctor   | architect  |
| Pet   | snake | fish | bird | guinea-pig |

