.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, taxi, car
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, rabbit, chinchilla
1. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the ship##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the owner of the bird is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Transport         | ship | taxi | car | helicopter |
| Pet   | rabbit          | bird     | chinchilla  | hedgehog     |

