.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, montecristo, pall-mall, siglo
There 4 different types of food: plum, kale, pumpkin, strawberry
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the siglo-smoker is between the person eating strawberry and the cain-smoker##2
3. the person eating kale is on the far right##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | cain | siglo | montecristo | pall-mall     |
| Food   | plum   | pumpkin    | strawberry   | kale |

