3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Hobby           | gardening | reading | video-games | hiking |
| Cigar   | bolivar   | baccarat | siglo         | fonseca |

