2. the fan country is on the far left##1
3. the accountant is between the fan country and the bartender##2
4. the project-manager is the fan country##1
5. the engineer is on the right of the fan techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Job       | project-manager | accountant | bartender | engineer |
| Music-Genre   | country    | soul  | techno    | d&b       |

