.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, mango, grapefruit, cranberry
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, orange, light-blue, grey
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person eating cranberry is the person who likes white##1
4. the person who likes grey is between the person eating strawberry and the person eating grapefruit##2
5. the person eating grapefruit is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | cranberry   | strawberry   | mango | grapefruit |
| Color         | white | orange | grey     | light-blue    |

