.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, baseball, golf, soccer
There 4 different types of food: lime, mango, orange, onion
1. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person eating lime and the person who's sport is soccer##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Sport   | golf    | soccer     | rowing | baseball |
| Food     | mango | onion | orange       | lime     |

 